This task focused on bridging the gap between individual technical practice and team collaboration. 
I utilized HackerRank to verify my Python fundamentals, finding the platform's instant feedback and badge system highly engaging for consistent skill-building. 
Additionally, I developed a Google Form quiz to assess and improve the digital literacy levels of my batchmates. 
Together, these tools provide a robust framework for both my academic development and my role in guiding others toward effective online collaboration.
